## 6. Parameter Mapping

Legacy parameters (0.0-10.0) are mapped to shader ranges:

| Parameter | Legacy Range | Shader Range | Mapping Formula |
|-----------|--------------|--------------|-----------------|
| `trail_decay` | 0-10 | 0.8-0.99 | `0.8 + (value/10) * 0.19` |
| `spectrum_height` | 0-10 | 0.1-1.0 | `0.1 + (value/10) * 0.9` |
| `frequency_bands` | 0-10 | 16-256 | `int(16 + (value/10) * 240)` |
| `color_mode` | 0-10 | 0-2 | `int(value/10 * 2)` (clamped to 2) |
| `trail_opacity` | 0-10 | 0.1-1.0 | `0.1 + (value/10) * 0.9` |

